# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Third-party media that is NOT owned by this project (kept out of the repo):
#  • public/data   — generated from the quran.com API by the scripts in scripts/
#                    (run `npm run setup:content` to regenerate it locally).
#  • public/adhan  — adhan recordings owned by their reciters; add licensed
#                    files locally. The app also streams audio, so it still runs.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
public/data/
public/adhan/

